{"tid":2405164,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"傳蘋果研發 Micro OLED 技術 將與台積電合作","createTime":"2021-02-12T07:07:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-12T09:48:02.000Z","uid":295230,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8b4848d9ae27003cdcddf0f7eeac33a3e38c1f97","tid":2405164,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T07:07:04.000Z","msg":"日經亞洲（Nikkei Asia）今天披露，蘋果公司（Apple）在台灣一處祕密基地，研發超先進顯示器技術Micro OLED，找上長期晶片供應夥伴台積電合作。<br />\n<br />\n報導引述消息人士表示，蘋果計畫研發 micro OLED 顯示器，這種顯示器面板直接建立在晶片的晶圓上，最終目標是把這種技術應用在未來推出的擴增實境裝置。<br />\n<br />\n知情人士透露，蘋果之所以找上台積電，是因為 Micro OLED 顯示器不像電視和手機的傳統 LCD 或高階智慧型手機的 OLED 螢幕是建立在玻璃基板上，而是直接建立在晶圓上，可讓顯示器更輕薄短小，耗電量更少，適用於穿戴式擴增實境裝置。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士表示，Micro OLED 計畫目前在試產階段，可能還要好幾年才能到量產階段。目前正在開發的顯示器大小不到 1 吋（2.54 公分）。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士表示，面板業者擅長生產大尺寸顯示器，但輕薄短小裝置，如擴增實境眼鏡，則需要小尺寸面板。蘋果之所以選擇台積電合作，主要是看重台積電在這方面的專業，同時蘋果也借重面板專家在顯示器方面的專業。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士表示，蘋果的 Micro OLED 部分零件將使用台積電現有晶片生產設備和製程。<br />\n<br />\n報導表示，這項計畫是在蘋果位於龍潭的一處祕密實驗室進行。除了 Micro OLED 顯示器外，蘋果也正在開發 Micro LED 技術，這兩種技術都已有試產的生產線。<br />\n<br />\n蘋果雇用友達光電數十名老手，同時也從日本和其他地方找來面板專家。消息人士告訴日經亞洲，所有參與這項計畫的人員必須簽訂嚴格的保密協議，甚至要求他們不得和在科技業任職的親友會面。<br />\n<br />\n台積電不願針對此報導置評，蘋果則未對一再置評要求做出回應。"},{"pid":"641b3c421be83655d4bd2ace09ee5924628fb53b","tid":2405164,"uid":73241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T07:07:18.000Z","msg":"如日"},{"pid":"d4c4f3fd99edc34d596c0e0601547666489b36a5","tid":2405164,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T07:07:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://technews.tw/2021/02/10/apple-tsmc-micro-led/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftechnews.tw%2F2021%2F02%2F10%2Fapple-tsmc-micro-led%2F&d=j8A0%2F5fiWOW2Etl1DmJ%2F%2FEBo7c%2BYFxEppcXi0rJe94o%3D&h=4ca2e2e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://technews.tw/2021/02/10/apple-tsmc-micro-led/</a>"},{"pid":"9de76ecfdd8d078fa196d6ba854154750341697f","tid":2405164,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"641b3c421be83655d4bd2ace09ee5924628fb53b","tid":2405164,"uid":73241,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T07:07:18.000Z","msg":"如日"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T07:07:36.000Z","msg":"bot<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b116940c397b0b5c13ffd4a5ebc4f6044bc6c40f","tid":2405164,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T07:08:03.000Z","msg":"我個bell爛啦教主<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56ee66aaa0badf5337db97ca4a2c319242af7c6e","tid":2405164,"uid":230594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T07:08:21.000Z","msg":"乜都插一腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df0253c54296e186d2e11c34a59f66dceaaae662","tid":2405164,"uid":295230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b116940c397b0b5c13ffd4a5ebc4f6044bc6c40f","tid":2405164,"uid":168366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T07:08:03.000Z","msg":"我個bell爛啦教主<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T07:12:18.000Z","msg":"唔好跟蹤我<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb845b3d150b15fa595a5e5babd1917797b1e4ae","tid":2405164,"uid":263261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T07:14:53.000Z","msg":"台積電股東<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62387fbabc913552c788b580a0ce63d4aaf5f4ad","tid":2405164,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T07:17:12.000Z","msg":"tsm上到140<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fc9095a0926bc0a27aecb22b6c2800b494cd0a1","tid":2405164,"uid":295230,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-12T07:17:54.000Z","msg":"石仔又要贏"},{"pid":"b618a95840c2858abe8f55e5fc3779f9b8d24ba2","tid":2405164,"uid":131078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"scor